data.description: Major Price adjustment!  MUST SEE !  Move-in ready.  Welcome to this beautiful and bright Single family home , nestled on a huge private lot in sought after Memorial Heights , Alexandria .   Expand this home to an even bigger multi family living space.  The convenient zoning of this home allows you to build additions!   you have an option to build another  living space on top of the existing spacious 2 car garage , or expand the existing house all the way to the next parcel which is being sold together.   first parcel has a residential dwelling in it with another structure which is a detached garage and storage,   and the other adjacent parcel is a lot with no structure in it . HOA free community ! Minutes from Old Town Alexandria and DC !  ADDRESSES:  📍2639 Memorial ST , Alexandria VA 22306   📍2637 Memorial St , Alexandria VA 22306
